# HomeOnInternet ‚Äî Architecture Overview

Personal site for Saumya Nayak built with **Next.js 13 Pages Router**, MDX blogs, custom CSS, and a mode-dial SPA-style navigation shell.

---

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 13 (Pages Router ‚Äî no App Router) |
| Styling | Custom CSS (`styles/site.css`) + Tailwind CSS 3 (`styles/globals.css`) |
| Content (blog) | MDX via `@next/mdx` + `@mdx-js/loader` |
| Font | Google Fonts ‚Äî Poppins + Hanken Grotesk (variable) |
| Route progress | `nprogress` |
| Sitemaps | `next-sitemap` |
| Deployment | Vercel |

